Mango Halwa💛

First day of school calls for something special – made his favourite Mango Halwa to celebrate 🥭🎒💛

SAVE IT TO TRY SOON

Ingredients:
1/2 cup ghee
1 cup sooji
4 cup hot water
1/2 cup mango pulp
1/2 cup sugar
2 tbsp milk + 8-10 strands of saffron (soak for 15mins)
1 tsp cardamom powder.
Garnish with some almonds, saffron ✨

latestPosts.caption:
Bharwan Tinde✨( Punjabi Style)

This is a delicious recipe of stuffed tinda or bharwan tinda where apple gourds aka tinda are made in an onion tomato based gravy.
I have used whole tinde for my recipe but they can be quartered or halved. Cooking time will vary as cut pieces will cook faster compared to whole tinde.

Ingredients:
500 gm Tinda
1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder
1 tsp Red Chilli powder
1 tsp Coriander powder
1/2 tsp salt
3/4 tsp Fennel Powder Coarsely
1/4 tsp Garam Masala
1/2 tsp amchur powder
3 tosp oil mustard oil
8-10 Black pepper corn
1 cinnamon stick
2 garlic cloves + 1/2 inch ginger
1 tomato
2 onion
2 green chill
1 tsp Cumin seeds
1 tosp sev
Salt to taste
Pinch of hing
Fresh coriander leaves
